+| `WorkflowBinService` | 1 new file + interface | Small (~60 lines) |
+| Script templates | Inline in service | Trivial |
+| Prompt template updates | 2 files (starter + resume) | Small (find/replace) |
+| OrchestrationService wiring | 1 edit | Trivial |
+| `withTestGraph` update | 1 edit | Trivial |
+| Tests | 1 new test file | Small (ensure creates files, scripts are executable, content is correct) |
+
+Total: **~150 lines of new code**, mostly template strings.
